description: This photo captures the serene morning atmosphere of Hackescher Markt station in Berlin. The sunlight streaming through the glass roof enhances the warm hues of the brickwork, creating an inviting scene. As the first rays of sun illuminate the platform, a calm, almost meditative ambiance is created, setting the tone before the city awakens. Hackescher Markt, with its architectural charm and peaceful morning light, embodies Berlin's timeless beauty.
